OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FPoliticians and employers in Guernsey
OL,7,Fare sounding alarm bells ahead of what
OL,8,Fthey describe as an impending
OL,9,F"employment crisis".
OL,11,FEmails leaked to ITV News reveal fears
OL,12,Fcirculating among local politicians of
OL,13,F"a train crash coming" in the next few
OL,14,Fweeks, when many of the island's
OL,15,Ftemporary workers will be forced to
OL,16,Fleave.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
