OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FIt comes as a lot of 'short-term
OL,7,Fpermits' (STEP) - the licences which
OL,8,Fallow people to move to work and live
OL,9,Fin Guernsey for three years - which
OL,10,Fwere granted under a series of
OL,11,Fpopulation management changes in April
OL,12,F2023, will soon expire.
OL,14,FThe emails further detail a backlog
OL,15,Fwith processing new STEP applications
OL,16,Fat the Population Management
OL,17,FDepartment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FWith many of the island's hospitality
OL,7,Fand social care staff employed on
OL,8,Fthese permits, employers are concerned
OL,9,Fthey will be left unable to replace
OL,10,Fthe staff they lose ahead of the busy
OL,11,Fsummer season.
OL,13,FGuernsey made major changes to its
OL,14,Fpopulation management in April 2023.
OL,16,FThe island used to have three housing
OL,17,Fpermits available:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FIn 2023, to rein in immigration and
OL,7,Fupdate the island's rules in the wake
OL,8,Fof Brexit, the medium-term permits
OL,9,Fwere scrapped.
OL,11,FGarin Dart, Chair of the Confederation
OL,12,Fof Guernsey Industry and Manager at Le
OL,13,FPommier Hotel, says the situation is
OL,14,Fworrying for employees and employers
OL,15,Falike.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,F"I think a lot of hoteliers are sad
OL,7,Fthat a lot of staff are being asked to
OL,8,Fleave when they've been on the island
OL,9,Fand contributing for so long", he
OL,10,Fexplains, adding that the current
OL,11,Fbacklog at Population Management means
OL,12,Fit can take up to 12 months to get new
OL,13,FSTEP licences through.
OL,15,F"If you're waiting for an answer -
OL,16,Fobviously on both sides, employers and
OL,17,Femployees - there's anxiety there over
OL,18,Fwhether you've got your licence, and
OL,19,Fhow long for."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FWill Haegeland, General Manager at the
OL,7,FPandora and Marton Hotels, says his
OL,8,Fbusiness is encountering similar
OL,9,Fdifficulties.
OL,11,F"I have staff who are coming to the
OL,12,Fend of their three years, which I then
OL,13,Fhave to start looking at 'how am I
OL,14,Fgoing to replace them?'", he explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,F"If we could employ local people, we
OL,7,Fwould - but every time we recruit, we
OL,8,Fdon't get any local applications. So
OL,9,Fwe have to go abroad and that
OL,10,Fobviously takes big costs, and a more
OL,11,Flengthy process to get people until
OL,12,Fthey can actually start working."
OL,14,FSome politicians are now floating the
OL,15,Fidea of extending those STEP licences
OL,16,Fdue to expire next month to four
OL,17,Fyears, giving the Population
OL,18,FManagement department time to clear
OL,19,Fthe backlog.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FDeputy Chris Blin says it is an
OL,7,Finterim solution he is "very much
OL,8,Fbehind".
OL,10,F"The worry is now that businesses are
OL,11,Fstruggling, and certain businesses
OL,12,Fhave key staff they need to extend",
OL,13,Fhe explains.
OL,15,F"So currently I've been working
OL,16,Falongside Population Management and
OL,17,Fthe President of Home Affairs to
OL,18,Fensure we do the best we can to find
OL,19,Fsolutions to make this work,
OL,20,Fespecially with the season right upon
OL,21,Fus."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FGarin and Will both say they would
OL,7,Falso be in favour of making this
OL,8,Fchange.
OL,10,F"One thing I raised with Population
OL,11,FManagement was if you had that extra
OL,12,Fyear, then that could be getting
OL,13,Fsomeone up to a managerial level with
OL,14,Fthat extra training, where they could
OL,15,Fthen be able to apply for a longer-
OL,16,Fterm licence", Garin explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,FWill agrees, adding, "As employers, we
OL,7,Fwant to have positive HR policies that
OL,8,Fcare about people. We want to develop
OL,9,Four people, and we want to retain
OL,10,Fthem. But here, we can't."
OL,12,FWhen asked about the possibility of an
OL,13,Fextension, Deputy Marc Leadbeater,
OL,14,FPresident of the Committee for Home
OL,15,FAffairs, said: "The last thing we
OL,16,Fwould want is to put undue pressure on
OL,17,Four valuable hospitality sector at the
OL,18,Fstart of the summer season, but the
OL,19,Fshort-term nature of a STEP is
OL,20,Ffundamental.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,F"Three years was previously identified
OL,7,Fas a red line, creating an inevitable
OL,8,Fchurn in the workforce, but with the
OL,9,Fopportunity still open to continue to
OL,10,Frecruit replacement staff from
OL,11,Foverseas if needed.
OL,13,F"Out of policy applications provide
OL,14,Fmuch-needed flexibility in the regime,
OL,15,Fbut it is important that this is only
OL,16,Fused in exceptional circumstances.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,F"At our meeting on Tuesday, we agreed
OL,7,Fto explore a temporary extension
OL,8,Fpolicy to the existing three-year STEP
OL,9,Fwhile a more comprehensive review of
OL,10,Fthe cap is considered as part of the
OL,11,Fplanned wider works on the population
OL,12,Fregime. We are also going to look at
OL,13,Fresourcing in the Population
OL,14,FManagement Office.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774353808
OL,3,C'Employment crisis' threatens
OL,4,CGuernsey's summer season
OL,6,F"While we are going into this work
OL,7,Fwith a genuinely open mind, STEPs are,
OL,8,Fas the name suggests, short-term, and
OL,9,Fso we'd encourage businesses with
OL,10,Fstaff coming to the end of a STEP to
OL,11,Fconsider starting recruitment
OL,12,Fprocesses in good time."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/13
